h="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a></figure></div><p>It now has competition from <strong><a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.rnselectastro&amp;hl=en_IN&amp;gl=US">Vama</a></strong> (Virtual Astrology and Mandir App). The name gives away a lot, but for redundancy&#8217;s sake, it&#8217;s an app that offers puja booking and live astrology services (along with consultations from vedic, tarot, and numerology experts). Vama <a href="https://inc42.com/buzz/vama-bags-1-5-mn-to-scale-its-virtual-astrology-temple-services/">raised 1.5mn USD</a> this month.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbebdcffe-10da-4f16-9921-fa26bf4dcf3e_872x322.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbebdcffe-10da-4f16-9921-fa26bf4dcf3e_872x322.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbebdcffe-10da-4f16-9921-fa26bf4dcf3e_872x322.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbebdcffe-10da-4f16-9921-fa26bf4dcf3e_872x322.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2